					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It goes to show I listen to a lot of Pogo, because that's exactly the vibe I got off that piece. Crazy.</p> <p>Anyway, I like this. Nice and haunting, and also, I note, the first Green King skip that isn't the King herself. (That's what the other one is, right?) The one thing I really like is you can see the outline of that kid's head under the dress, and that doesn't make it any less creepy.</p> <blockquote> <p>in which sound reflects off as if there was a physical barrier.</p> </blockquote> <p>You should remove 'in' and also a 'the the' later on.</p> 
				 	]]>
