					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1043094#post-2137079</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1043094/scp-2530#post-2137079</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 22 Oct 2014 09:37:18 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Accelerando</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1599414</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This article includes a lot of stuff that isn't mine.</p> <ul> <li>The first image is from <a href="http://imgur.com/LNW8hXB">samuirai</a> on reddit.</li> <li>2nd image by Roger Ballen, called <em>Head Inside Shirt</em>, from his book <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Shadow Chamber</span>. Website found <a href="http://www.rogerballen.com/image-gallery/shadow-chamber-images">here</a>. Permission was requested and received to use this.</li> <li>Music by Riverman, remix of &quot;Whisperlude&quot; by Pogo. <em>Download the entire song <a href="https://rivermanmusic.bandcamp.com/track/pogo-whisperlude-riverman-remix">here</a></em>, or his 4 other remixes <a href="https://rivermanmusic.bandcamp.com/album/pogo-remixes-ep">here</a>, and see all of Pogo's work on his <a href="https://soundcloud.com/pogomix">soundcloud</a> or <a href="http://pogomix.net/">site</a>. Permission also recieved by Riverman.</li> <li>Also, the song lyrics are based off the tune of &quot;<a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tBkkplOiSjQ">Lakehouse</a>&quot; by Of Monsters and Men. Don't try to sing along, I've edited it to avoid the repetition already prominent in the original song.</li> </ul> <p>Thanks to Eskobar, Roget, Von Pincier, TwistedGears, and Zolgamax for feedback. Also, this is the prequel to <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1530">SCP-1530</a>.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
